              "type": "explain",
              "text": "You’ll also see **rule-based** and **time-of-day** controls. Rule-based uses rules like 'deny if source country is X' or 'require MFA when risk is high'. Time-of-day restricts access based on hours/days (helpful for contractors or risky admin actions)."
