        {
          "id": "ch8-m05-p01",
          "title": "Account types you must recognize",
          "content_blocks": [
            {
              "type": "explain",
              "text": "Security+ loves account types:\n- **User accounts** (people)\n- **Service accounts** (apps/services)\n- **Privileged/admin accounts** (high impact)\n- **Guest/temporary accounts** (limited)\n- **Shared accounts** (generally bad for accountability)\nDifferent account types need different controls, especially logging and privilege boundaries."
