          "content_blocks": [
            {
              "type": "explain",
              "text": "Exam-safe separation:\n- **SAML**: federation for SSO, uses assertions (often enterprise).\n- **OAuth**: *authorization* delegation (app gets permission to act on your behalf).\n- **OpenID Connect (OIDC)**: *authentication* layer built on OAuth (identity tokens)."
