          "title": "MFA factors and implementations",
          "content_blocks": [
            {
              "type": "explain",
              "text": "MFA combines **two or more factors**: something you know (password), have (token/phone), are (biometric), do (behavior), or where you are (location). Implementation matters: push prompts, hardware keys, smart cards—each has different risk to phishing and prompt fatigue."
